Vehement/Unicron/Reflector/Sun Crusher/Shockwave:


Vehement easily shifted to the left, the electromagnetic pulses going past 
him easily.  Two optic blasts were sent to intercept the missiles, shrapnel 
striking his abdomen.

Raising his left arm, he launched two energy-signature seeking missiles at 
Killfest, and two more from the other arm at FZ.

---

Reflector fired an optic blast at the jet pack before it even got three 
meters from EndBringer.  Raising an arm, he launched a heat seeking missile 
at FZ.

---

Unicron raised an arm, launching two energy-signature seeking missiles.

---

Sun Crusher felt two missiles hit his armor, not penetrating the thick armor 
plating.  The mounted machien gun swerved, firing off 25 armor-piercing 
rounds at Greven.

The smaller cannon swerved, launching off a sonic arc at Greven's legs.

The larger cannon fired off another three sonic shells at the Cybertronian 
Fire.

---

Shockwave launched another two missiles down at the Cybertronian Fire, flying 
in an arc to get another shot off.
